snippet.title: Kurt Hugo Schneider
snippet.description:
Hey, I'm Kurt, a music producer and filmmaker. Watch a video and if you like it, subscribe! Deal? :1 

Business Contact ONLY:
KurtSchneiderBusiness (at) gmail.com

(I love you guys, but really only business stuff to that email ;)

Send me links to videos of YOU singing at KurtHugoSchneiderMusic@yahoo.com

Thank you to all guys who have subscribed, shared our videos, and given your support from day 1.  Wouldn't be here without you!

Rock on! 
kurt :1
